        "created_at": "2019-02-07T02:09:01.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=2113066\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>2013 Henri Germain et Fils Meursault 1er Cru Charmes</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Meursault 1er Cru (2/6/2019)</em><br>\nThis is a stunning wine. It has dropped the \u201choney flavored\u201d reduction now. Intense. Extremely mineral in character. Penetrating. Coming into a great window for drinking.<br>\nThe nose might improve but the palate is wonderful. Spicy. Complex. Very fresh. One of the best 2013 whites.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
