        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/mike_grammer/{size}/335107_2.png",
        "created_at": "2019-02-07T16:46:04.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Looking forward to a 13 PYCM (can\u2019t remember if it\u2019s a Chassagne or Puligny\u2026I\u2019m picking it up when I head down to SoCal) that I will likely open sometime next weekend.  Don\u2019t know this producer at all, so much thanks for your notes, Don and Alan.</p>\n<p>Mike</p>",
